#ColorAtom

Fast and Furious, Honor and glory! Play with global players and fight for your self! 

There are much colorful atom with positive or negative energy in our universe. In order to survive, you must use your "positive atom" to fight against "negative atom". You have 10 "positive atom" at first, and then shoot them by swiping up on the screen. When you eliminate a "negative atom", more "positive atom" will be given to you as the reward. But if there is a "negative atom" rush into your baseline, you will lose much "positive atom" as punishment. Remember that "positive atom" is your life, if you have no "positive atom": game over!

You can pause the game by swiping down on the screen.

